ight=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-5 h-5 text-gray-300\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></button></div><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-dark-card transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><div class=\"min-h-screen py-12 px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><h1 class=\"text-5xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4\">Community Rules</h1><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-lg\">Guidelines for a respectful and welcoming community</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-8 h-8 text-neon-pink\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Our Community Philosophy</h2></div><p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">Anime Hub Novi Sad is built on respect, inclusivity, and shared passion. These rules help ensure our community remains a welcoming space for all anime fans, regardless of their background, experience level, or preferences. By participating in our community, you agree to follow these guidelines.</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-8 h-8 text-neon-purple\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Core Principles</h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-neon-pink/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1\"><span class=\"text-neon-pink font-bold\">1</span></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Respect Everyone</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Treat all community members with dignity and respect, regardless of their opinions, background, or experience level with anime.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-neon-purple/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1\"><span class=\"text-neon-purple font-bold\">2</span></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Be Inclusive</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Welcome newcomers and experienced fans alike. Different opinions and perspectives make our community richer.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-neon-blue/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1\"><span class=\"text-neon-blue font-bold\">3</span></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Constructive Dialogue</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Disagreements are natural, but keep discussions civil. Focus on ideas, not personal attacks.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-neon-green/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1\"><span class=\"text-neon-green font-bold\">4</span></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Protect Privacy</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Never share personal information about others without consent. Respect everyone&#x27;s privacy boundaries.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-alert-triangle w-8 h-8 text-neon-red\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Prohibited Behavior</h2></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-5 h-5 text-neon-red\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg>Harassment &amp; Bullying</h3><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-400 ml-6\"><li>No personal attacks, threats, or harassment of any kind</li><li>No stalking or unwanted attention toward other members</li><li>No hate speech, slurs, or discriminatory language</li><li>No doxxing or sharing private information</li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square w-5 h-5 text-neon-red\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg>Inappropriate Content</h3><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-400 ml-6\"><li>No NSFW or explicit content unless clearly marked and in appropriate sections</li><li>No spam, excessive self-promotion, or commercial advertising</li><li>No illegal content or links to illegal activities</li><li>No malware, viruses, or harmful links</li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye w-5 h-5 text-neon-red\"><path d=\"M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>Event Misconduct</h3><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-400 ml-6\"><li>No disruption of events or meetups</li><li>No harassment of event staff or attendees</li><li>No unauthorized recording or photography where prohibited</li><li>No theft or vandalism at event venues</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square w-8 h-8 text-neon-blue\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Content Guidelines</h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-300\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-neon-green rounded-full mt-2\"></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Fan Art &amp; Creative Content</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Share your creative work in the Showcase section. Always credit original creators and respect copyright laws.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-neon-green rounded-full mt-2\"></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Discussion Posts</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Keep discussions relevant to anime and community interests. Use appropriate categories and tags.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-neon-green rounded-full mt-2\"></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Spoilers</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Always use spoiler tags for major plot points. Be considerate of those who haven&#x27;t seen the latest episodes.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-neon-green rounded-full mt-2\"></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Self-Promotion</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Limited self-promotion of anime-related content is allowed in appropriate sections. Excessive promotion will be removed.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-8 h-8 text-neon-purple\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Enforcement &amp; Consequences</h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-300\"><p>Our admin team reserves the right to enforce these rules through:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-6\"><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Warnings:</strong> First violations typically receive a warning</li><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Content Removal:</strong> Inappropriate content will be removed</li><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Temporary Bans:</strong> Repeated violations may result in temporary suspension</li><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Permanent Bans:</strong> Severe or repeated violations may result in permanent removal</li></ul><p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-400\">Appeals can be submitted to the admin team through our WhatsApp group or email.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900/50 to-pink-900/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-neon-purple/30 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 text-neon-pink\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">Questions About Rules?</h2><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-6\">If you&#x27;re unsure about whether something is allowed, or if you need to report a violation, please contact our admin team.</p><a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/KqoazdpQWWQGkxMBkBLR56\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"btn-primary inline-flex items-center\">Contact Admin Team</a></div></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-dark-card border-t border-dark-border mt-auto\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 